<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="congratulate-vt">congratulate <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kən'grætʃuleɪt/    美 /kən'grætʃuleɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>祝贺；向…道喜：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The two sportsmen <strong>congratulated</strong> each other <strong>on</strong> winning the match by shaking hands.
两位运动员相互握手祝贺对方赢得比赛。</p><footer>2008 上海</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’d like to <strong>congratulate</strong> you <strong>on</strong> your wonderful performance.
我对您的精彩表演表示祝贺。</p></div></div>